These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  social-worker, nurse, chef, scientist, architect
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, april, march, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
3. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
4. the chef is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the social-worker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the architect is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the scientist is on the left or right of the architect##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Job          | nurse | social-worker | architect | scientist | chef |
| Birthday   | march  | september      | august   | january     | april    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, electriciancher, entrepreneur, electrician, police-officer
There are 5 different nationalities: british, pakistani, dutch, canadian, egyptian
1. the software-developer is in an even position##4
2. the software-developer is on the right of the canadian##1
3. the police-officer is in the middle##1
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
5. the british is between the entrepreneur and the canadian##2
6. the dutch is on the right of the software-developer##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the left of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Job   | entrepreneur     | electrician       | police-officer    | software-developer | electriciancher   |
| Nationality      | pakistani | british | canadian | egyptian      | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, cherry, pomegranate, onion, orange
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, satire, scientific, crime, epic
1. the person watching crime movies is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
8. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Food         | watermelon | pomegranate | cherry | onion    | orange |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | superhero        | scientific      | satire | epic      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, nurse, software-developer, manager, teacher
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, cola, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
1. the software-developer is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
4. the teacher is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the nurse is between the person drinking cola and the teacher##2
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Job         | firefighter      | manager | software-developer | nurse   | teacher  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk    | cola        | sprite | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, tiparillo, bongani, old-henry, blend
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking, board-games, traveling, cooking
1. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
8. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Cigar      | blend      | tiparillo | dunhill   | old-henry  | bongani  |
| Hobby   | board-games | traveling | magic-tricks | woodworking | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, yellow, pink, purple, green
5 different pets are kept: pony, goat, frog, fish, dog
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the dog and the person who likes pink##2
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the owner of the frog is the person who likes pink##1
6. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
7. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Color   | yellow        | red                | purple  | pink  | green            |
| Pet        | pony | dog | goat | frog | fish |

