.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
City: rome, paris, berlin, colone, boston
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, siglo, bluemaster, cain, davidoff
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
3. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
9. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| City   | boston       | berlin   | paris    | colone    | rome |
| Cigar        | bluemaster | bongani | siglo | davidoff | cain     |

