.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish, guinea-pig, hamster, cat
House: victorian, futuristic, colonial, cape-cod, gothic-revival
1. the colonial house is the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the victorian house is between the cape-cod house and the gothic-revival house##2
6. the colonial house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
7. the colonial house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Pet      | guinea-pig  | goldfish       | fish      | hamster  | cat   |
| House   | gothic-revival | victorian | cape-cod | futuristic | colonial |

