.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
House: modern, palace, art-deco, victorian, tower
City: liverpool, boston, marseilles, edinburgh, venice
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
2. the victorian house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the victorian house##1
4. the victorian house is on the far right##1
5. the palace house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the art-deco house is between the palace house and the modern house##2
7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the art-deco house##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| House   | tower | palace | art-deco     | modern | victorian |
| City           | boston | liverpool     | marseilles | venice    | edinburgh      |

