There are 5 different nationalities: russian, italian, brazilian, indonesian, dutch
1. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the italian is the person drinking juice##1
4. the russian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | iced-tea | mirinda | juice | sprite |
| Nationality   | brazilian | dutch | indonesian    | italian    | russian  |

