.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
City: miami, marseilles, rome, nizza, hamburg
5 different pets are kept: cat, snake, guinea-pig, turtle, bird
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
3. the person traveling to miami is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the snake##2
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to rome##1
6. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| City    | marseilles    | hamburg  | miami      | nizza     | rome |
| Pet   | cat | snake | turtle | guinea-pig | bird |

