.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, funk, salsa, blues, indie
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, ivory, black, coral, pink
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes pink is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who likes pink is in the middle##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes pink and the fan of funk##2
7. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4
8. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre        | blues | indie | r&b  | salsa | funk     |
| Color   | ivory  | black     | pink | brown      | coral |

