.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, ferret, fish, goat
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, airplane, van, bus
1. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person driving the motorbike and the owner of the ferret##2
7. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Pet      | goat       | ferret | chinchilla | fish   | rabbit   |
| Transport   | van | trike | bus  | motorbike | airplane |

