.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge, go
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, black, red, coral, orange
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
7. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes black and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game    | go   | bridge  | mah-jongg     | monopoly | backgammon |
| Color   | light-blue | red | orange | coral | black      |

