.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, scientist, electrician, software-developer, librarian
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, art-deco, colonial, victorian
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the doctor is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the doctor##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the electrician is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
8. the colonial house is in the middle##1
9. the cape-cod house is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Job   | scientist  | electrician    | software-developer | doctor   | librarian |
| House   | victorian | cape-cod | colonial    | gothic-revival | art-deco |

