2. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
3. the palace house is on the far right##1
4. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
6. the modern house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
