.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, juice, tea, lemonade
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot, lavender, green, amber
1. the person drinking tea is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who likes yellow##2
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Beverage   | cola | tea | juice     | lemonade     | mirinda |
| Color     | green   | apricot   | yellow | lavender | amber  |

