.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
City: prague, berlin, miami, nizza, paris
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, cooking, magic-tricks, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
9. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| City   | prague | berlin | paris     | miami | nizza |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks       | sudoku   | cooking | reading   | gardening        |

