.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
5 different games are played: chess, domino, go, backgammon, canasta
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, green, brown, yellow
1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes green is the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing chess and the person who likes yellow##2
6. the person who likes orange is between the person playing backgammon and the person who likes yellow##2
7. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
8. the person who likes yellow is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Game         | backgammon | go | domino | canasta | chess     |
| Color   | brown    | orange   | yellow       | green | fuchsia |

