.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, electrician, mechanic, doctor, social-worker
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, fonseca, aristoff, cain, prince
1. the cain-smoker is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the social-worker##1
5. the doctor is in the middle##1
6. the prince-smoker is the designer##1
7. the electrician is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Job   | designer | mechanic      | doctor | social-worker     | electrician      |
| Cigar     | prince | fonseca | cain | alhambra | aristoff |

 